description: Today´s mission took me to the outskirts of Prague. After almost one hour drive I finally reached an area where obviously no-one really would want to live. Large communist buildings; each of them built for hundreds of families. Even the doorbell wasn´t working. So I had to wait a couple of minutes until today´s "client" showed up to open me the door. His apartment was basically a small room as he shared the flat with 2 mates to share the costs. And as he moved in just recently he didn´t even have a bed. Instead he had a lot of debts. Not actually that much -but some of them were private-debts which were already overdue. He was a straight guy in his mid-twenties working in a tattoo-studio. A real challenge to get my "client´s" ass this time.
title: Debt Dandy 85
